{"tid":936269,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角嚴重交通意外《事後檢討 》","createTime":"2018-12-10T15:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T03:49:53.000Z","uid":28860,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b7666eb340f99e23ac3fc4df0d5d94c3f95826","tid":936269,"uid":28860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"與其喺度屌d賓賓路人警察司機，不如講番啲真正可以防止悲劇再次發生嘅嘢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如根據今次意外警惕啲未考牌同考咗牌嘅司機防止悲劇再次發生.<br />\n1. 停車記得拉實個hand brake<br />\n2. 軚盤要扭向路邊&nbsp;<br />\n3. 入反方向波箱 如車頭向下入後波<br />\n4. 大車要攝磚<br />\n5. 定期check 車<br />\n<br />\n警察方面係唔係應該可以出告票 ,告一啲冇做足安全措施,如拍喺斜路軚盤冇扭向路邊或大車沒攝磚嘅司機,就好似依加捉違泊咁,警惕返佢哋要做足上述安全措施.<br />\n<br />\n汽車製造商方面又可唔可以有技術,可以令到啲車唔插匙就自動鎖車轆, 如有特殊情況例如要拖車,先另外有掣可以解鎖咁又得唔得呢? 當然佢哋係專業應該另有考慮, 而係我哋呢啲普通人唔識.<br />\n<br />\n(利申冇車牌,歡迎各位識揸車嘅巴打絲打分享同詳細講解安全守則.)<br />\n集思廣益,唔希望再有同類型悲劇發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8ee17a91581eea543c6d75c7cb97dabe97d48c","tid":936269,"uid":28860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f26f119e2e3526ea73a1407a9e017d940b49360","tid":936269,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/FKCxcS0T/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FF